{subhead}Paraglide still on?{def}
{left}
{p} {p}
The long awaited 3D addon for the PicassoIV is a step closer today, as
Blittersoft http://www.blittersoft.com/ have announced:
{p} {p}
"We have this week received news with confirmation of the ParaGlide
project.  We have been urged to keep pre-orders open so if you wish to
secure your unit on release, be sure to pre-order now!"
